                                                                                              NIST SP 800-213A                                             GUIDANCE FOR THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT
                                                                                                                                                  IOT DEVICE CYBERSECURITY REQUIREMENT CATALOG

                                                                                                                      • The ways in which security and oversight requirements are included
                                                                                                                        within contracts with entities throughout the supply chain for the IoT
                                                                                                                        device.
                                                                                                                      • Remote monitoring activities the manufacturer performs for each of
                                                                                                                        the supporting entities' activities.
                                                                                                                      • Description of the other access and data collection, use and sharing
                                                                                                                        activities the supporting entities perform in support of the IoT devices,
                                                                                                                        and how the manufacturer provides monitoring for these activities.
                                                                                                            c. Communications and documentation detailing how the IoT device supports
